    "block_shuffle_leading_term (sanity-check: shuffle leading_term within (rank, decade) cells; per-cell M_k is invariant by construction, so this is actually a Pattern 7 calibration \u2014 verifies pipeline)",
    "katz_sarnak_vs_rank (verify rank-0 leading_term distribution matches SO_even central-value distribution; rank-1 matches SO_odd derivative)",
